<a href='http://blog.nonsensebb.com/2011/09/03/gundam-0080-war-in-the-pocket/gundam0088-1/' title='Mobile Suit Gundam 0080: War in the Pocket - Eyecatch'><img width="150" height="100" src="http://blog.nonsensebb.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/09/gundam0088-1-150x100.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail" alt="Mobile Suit Gundam 0080: War in the Pocket - Eyecatch" title="Mobile Suit Gundam 0080: War in the Pocket - Eyecatch" /></a>

